subject: Basketball
lead_paragraph: Winless in two tries against ranked teams after opening the season with seven wins against weak opponents, No. 21 Syracuse fell to No. 22 Oklahoma State, 72-68. No. 14  Arizona defeated Louisville, 72-65, in the second game.
